OL,3,CThousands of civil servants to leave
OL,4,CLondon as government cuts costs
OL,6,FThousands more civil servant jobs are
OL,7,Fset to be moved out of London as the
OL,8,Fgovernment seeks to cut costs and move
OL,9,Fmore decision-making out of Whitehall.
OL,11,FUnder plans to "radically reform the
OL,12,Fstate", the government has announced
OL,13,Fit will reduce the number of civil
OL,14,Fservants working in the capital by
OL,15,F12,000, shifting jobs to a series of
OL,16,Fnew regional "campuses" across the
OL,17,Fcountry.
