OL,3,CThousands of civil servants to leave
OL,4,CLondon as government cuts costs
OL,6,FThe changes will also see 11
OL,7,Fgovernment office buildings close,
OL,8,Fincluding one of its largest
OL,9,FWestminster sites, in a move expected
OL,10,Fto save #94 million a year on London's
OL,11,Fexpensive rental and leasing costs by
OL,12,F2032.
OL,14,FGovernment departments will be
OL,15,Fexpected to submit plans for
OL,16,Frelocating staff, including senior
OL,17,Fcivil servants, as part of the
OL,18,Fspending review due to be completed on
OL,19,FJune 11.
