OL,6,FAmong the offices being closed in
OL,7,FLondon is 102 Petty France, one of the
OL,8,Flargest government offices in the
OL,9,Fcapital and home to around 7,000 civil
OL,10,Fservants in the Ministry of Justice,
OL,11,FHM Courts and Tribunal Service, Crown
OL,12,FProsecution Service and the Government
OL,13,FLegal Department.
OL,15,FThe government will also close 39
OL,16,FVictoria Street, which has been home
OL,17,Fto the Department of Health and Social
OL,18,FCare since the end of 2017.
