OL,4,CLondon as government cuts costs
OL,6,FMcFadden said: "By relocating
OL,7,Fthousands of Civil Service roles, we
OL,8,Fwill not only save taxpayers money, we
OL,9,Fwill make this government one that
OL,10,Fbetter reflects the country it serves."
OL,12,F"As we radically reform the state, we
OL,13,Fare going to make it much easier for
OL,14,Ftalented people everywhere to join the
OL,15,FCivil Service and help us rebuild
OL,16,FBritain," he added.
