OL,6,FAround 80% of civil servants ` more
OL,7,Fthan 400,000 people ` already work
OL,8,Foutside London, but the most senior
OL,9,Fmandarins tend to be based in the
OL,10,Fcapital.
OL,12,FUnder Wednesday's proposals, half of
OL,13,Fsenior civil service roles would be
OL,14,Fbased outside London by 2030.
OL,16,FProspect union general secretary Mike
OL,17,FClancy welcomed the plans to "increase
OL,18,Fand empower" civil servants based
OL,19,Foutside London, but called for more
OL,20,Fclarity on the role of arm's-length
OL,21,Fbodies outside the capital.
